{"blogid": "123172514", "writerAge": "码龄1年", "writerBlogNum": "27", "writerCollect": "170", "writerComment": "4", "writerFan": "10", "writerGrade": "3级", "writerIntegral": "574", "writerName": "a_small_cherry", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_123172514.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "110615", "writerRankWeekly": "493242", "writerThumb": "20", "writerVisitNum": "102544", "blog_read_count": "781", "blog_time": "于 2022-02-28 15:12:21 发布", "blog_title": "Centos7安装PHP", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">​</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"> 阿里云官方镜像站：<a href=\"https://developer.aliyun.com/mirror/?utm_content=g_1000307095\" title=\"阿里巴巴开源镜像站-OPSX镜像站-阿里云开发者社区\">阿里巴巴开源镜像站-OPSX镜像站-阿里云开发者社区</a></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">我们在系统安装软件时都会遇到各种小问题，那么如何才能提高我们在云服务器上的软件安装效率呢？接下来就为大家详细介绍下如何在 CentOS 环境下通过 yum 命令快速安装软件。</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"560\" src=\"image\\ade9724b384a4dbea6a31dba6ca92b6f.png\" width=\"792\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">在 CentOS 环境下，我们可以通过 yum 命令快速安装软件。对于 yum 下载源，我们不需要添加任何软件源，就可以直接安装软件包。</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">yum install 软件名称</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">在安装软件的过程中，系统将自动搜索相关的软件包和依赖关系，并在界面中提示用户确认搜索到的软件包是否合适。在这里我们将以 PHP 为例，进行详细说明。</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:left;\">更新yum源（默认yum源中无php） rpm -Uvh <a href=\"http://mirror.webtatic.com/yum/el6/latest.rpm\" title=\"http://mirror.webtatic.com/yum/el6/latest.rpm\">http://mirror.webtatic.com/yum/el6/latest.rpm</a></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:left;\">（暂未找到阿里云yum源，先用其它代替）</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"147\" src=\"image\\3fafef3597424186b27ef19672a1da7c.png\" width=\"784\"/><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"image\\15d07962889942da961bd4819d689ac7.png\" width=\"1\"/>​</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">执行 yum -y install php 命令，安装 PHP 后，界面显示如下图：</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"529\" src=\"image\\2bf368a8308542bebab414272dbb5fac.png\" width=\"788\"/><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"image\\015a981753fa4dc38f95d8de4a0140a5.png\" width=\"1\"/>​</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"> 查看php安装了那些拓展模块 php -m</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"523\" src=\"image\\8b6ea144f91e45f195995bee2df4f941.png\" width=\"781\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">你也可以执行以下命令，查看软件包的版本信息</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">rpm -q 软件名</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"image\\75ddbc4c990c4750afd3f2f4206e64b6.png\" width=\"1\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">比如执行 rpm -q php ，如下图所示：</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"><img alt=\"\" height=\"62\" src=\"image\\2f1d0ec68b6049f0b8b7c88c920999b8.png\" width=\"317\"/> <img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"image\\c417a7ff1699404189c236a92eaf3b5d.png\" width=\"1\"/>​</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:0;text-align:justify;\">​</p>\n</div>\n</div>"}